|blank_name = |blank_info = }} Te Awamutu is a town in the Waipa District of the North Island, New Zealand. It is 30 kilometers south of Hamilton on State Highway 3. It is birth place of Crowded House and Split Enz singers Neil Finn and Tim Finn. == References == Category:Towns in Waikato Category:Waipa District
